 Racers compete during the Egypt Desert Challenge Rally held in the desert of Fayoum, Egypt, on March 11, 2022. The Egypt Desert Challenge Rally 2022 is held from March 11 to 12 in Fayoum. Racers from some 15 Egyptian teams showed their desert racing skill on the first day of the rally, which is held to stimulate local sports tourism in the desert. (Xinhua/Ahmed Gomaa)  Racers compete during the Egypt Desert Challenge Rally held in the desert of Fayoum, Egypt, on March 11, 2022. The Egypt Desert Challenge Rally 2022 is held from March 11 to 12 in Fayoum. Racers from some 15 Egyptian teams showed their desert racing skill on the first day of the rally, which is held to stimulate local sports tourism in the desert. (Xinhua/Ahmed Gomaa)  Racers compete during the Egypt Desert Challenge Rally held in the desert of Fayoum, Egypt, on March 11, 2022. The Egypt Desert Challenge Rally 2022 is held from March 11 to 12 in Fayoum. Racers from some 15 Egyptian teams showed their desert racing skill on the first day of the rally, which is held to stimulate local sports tourism in the desert. (Xinhua/Ahmed Gomaa)  Racers compete during the Egypt Desert Challenge Rally held in the desert of Fayoum, Egypt, on March 11, 2022. The Egypt Desert Challenge Rally 2022 is held from March 11 to 12 in Fayoum. Racers from some 15 Egyptian teams showed their desert racing skill on the first day of the rally, which is held to stimulate local sports tourism in the desert. (Xinhua/Ahmed Gomaa)  Racers compete during the Egypt Desert Challenge Rally held in the desert of Fayoum, Egypt, on March 11, 2022. The Egypt Desert Challenge Rally 2022 is held from March 11 to 12 in Fayoum. Racers from some 15 Egyptian teams showed their desert racing skill on the first day of the rally, which is held to stimulate local sports tourism in the desert. (Xinhua/Ahmed Gomaa)